<title>KHRIHFA, MANG THA CH439</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka dawt te it law dai tein i din, Na Khamhtu tang cungah na lu chia
 tuah, Kannih nakin Jesuh nih an dawt deuh, Mangtha! Mangtha! Mangtha!

[V2]
 Ngakchia te bang dai tein it ko tuah, Ngaih-chiatnak nih an hlau kho
 ti lai lo, Zungzal dong lo dinhnak tha na phan cang, Mangtha! Mangtha!
 Mangtha!

[V3]
 Vawlei in muihnak a loh dih hlan tiang, Caan dongh tikah a kan khawmh
 dih hlan tiang, Khua ceu maw vialte an loh dih hlan tiang, Mangtha!
 Mangtha! Mangtha!

[V4]
 Dawtnak thiang nih dawh in an ser hlan tiang, Pathian na lawhnak ni
 bang a tlang lai, Sui luchin cu nang caah a put lai, Mangtha! Mangtha!
 Mangtha!

[V5]
 A thutdan hmaiah kan i tong than lai, A thil pekmi zong kan i thuam te
 lai, A kan hngalh bang kannih kan hngalh hlan tiang, Mangtha! Mangtha!
 Mangtha!</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
</song>